                  <a class="award" href="/award/show/40-j-gordon-coogler-award">J. Gordon Coogler Award for the worst book of the year (2004)</a>, <a class="award" href="/award/show/6395-puddly-award">Puddly Award for Nonfiction (2005)</a>, <a class="award" href="/award/show/32007-thurber-prize">Thurber Prize for American Humor (2005)</a>
