<span id="freeTextContainer12125058070641561726">If you are at all familiar with The Daily Show With John Stewart, then you pretty much know what this book will be like. Two notes: <br/><br/>(1) The book is also a parody of school textbooks, from the obvious (and great) &quot;Classroom Activities&quot; at the end of each chapter to more subtle touches like the <b>bold text</b> used for key vocabulary words.<br/><br/>(2) There is a fair amount of profanity, sometimes used well but sometimes a jarring attempt at a cheap laugh. </span>
